<%= open_graph_tags title: t(".title"), description: t(".description"), image: image_url("opengraph/affiliates.png") %>

<div class="container overflow-hidden max-w-5xl py-24 mx-auto">
  <div class="text-base leading-7 text-red-950">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <h1 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-red-900 sm:text-4xl"><%= t(".title") %></h1>
    <p class="mt-6 text-xl leading-8"><%= t(".description") %></p>
    <div class="mt-10 flex">
      <%= link_to "Sign up for an account", new_affiliate_path, class: "bg-red-600 px-3.5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-red-700 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-indigo-600" %>
    </div>

    <!-- Details -->
    <div class="mt-10 max-w-2xl">
      <h2 class="mt-16 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-red-900">How much can I make?</h2>
      <p class="mt-6">Quebec Dev charges businesses $99 for a monthly subscription and a 5% hiring fee for full-time employees. If you refer a business that subscribes for 3 months and hires a developer at $150,000 <span class="font-semibold">you will make about $390</span>.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- How it works -->
    <div class="mt-10 max-w-2xl">
      <h2 class="mt-16 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-red-900">How it works</h2>
      <ol role="list" class="mt-8 max-w-xl space-y-8 text-red-950">
        <li class="flex flex-col">
          <strong class="font-semibold text-red-900">Step 1</strong>
          Sign up for a Quebec Dev account. You don't need to create a developer or business profile and it's free to join.
        </li>
        <li class="flex flex-col">
          <strong class="font-semibold text-red-900">Step 2</strong>
          You'll receive a unique referral URL via email. Use this in your website footer, podcast, newsletter, and social media posts. Or share it directly with your hiring manager!
        </li>
        <li class="flex flex-col">
          <strong class="font-semibold text-red-900">Step 3</strong>
          Get paid 5% recurring commissions. Youâ€™ll get paid for every month your referral is a paying customer of Quebec Dev.
        </li>
      </ol>
      <p class="mt-8">Commissions include the monthly subscription fee <em>and</em> hiring fees. If your referral hires a developer for $150,000 you will receive $375 - 5% of the <%= link_to "5% hiring fee", pricing_path, class: "font-semibold underline" %>.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Rules -->
    <div class="mt-10 max-w-2xl">
      <h2 class="mt-16 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-red-900">Program rules</h2>
      <ol role="list" class="mt-8 max-w-xl space-y-2 text-red-950">
        <li>You can't refer yourself.</li>
        <li>You <em>can</em> refer your hiring manager, CTO, HR department, etc.</li>
        <li>No ads and no pretending to be an employee.</li>
      </ol>
      <p class="mt-8">Questions? <%= link_to "Send us an email", "mailto:#{Rails.application.config.emails.support}", class: "font-semibold underline" %>.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQs -->
    <div class="mt-10 max-w-2xl">
      <h2 class="mt-16 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-red-900">FAQs</h2>
      <dl class="mt-8 space-y-8">
        <div>
          <dt>
            <span class="text-base font-semibold leading-7">How do I get paid?</span>
          </dt>
          <dd class="mt-2">
            <p class="text-base leading-7 text-red-950">Commission fees pay out on the first business day of each month. Affiliates are paid via PayPal and have no minimums to hit before you receive your money.</p>
          </dd>
        </div>

        <div>
          <dt>
            <span class="text-base font-semibold leading-7">How do I track my referrals?</span>
          </dt>
          <dd class="mt-2">
            <p class="text-base leading-7 text-red-950"><%= link_to "Email us", "mailto:#{Rails.application.config.emails.support}", class: "font-semibold underline" %> for information about your referrals.</p>
          </dd>
        </div>

        <div>
          <dt>
            <span class="text-base font-semibold leading-7">What if I forgot to ask someone to use my URL?</span>
          </dt>
          <dd class="mt-2">
            <p class="text-base leading-7 text-red-950"><%= link_to "Email us", "mailto:#{Rails.application.config.emails.support}", class: "font-semibold underline" %> who you referred and when and the conversion will be manually attributed to you so you get paid.</p>
          </dd>
        </div>

        <div>
          <dt>
            <span class="text-base font-semibold leading-7">Do I get money for referring developers?</span>
          </dt>
          <dd class="mt-2">
            <p class="text-base leading-7 text-red-950">Not currently. You'll only get affiliate fees for referring businesses that sign up for paid subscriptions.</p>
          </dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer CTA -->
    <div class="py-24">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-red-900 sm:text-4xl">Ready to partner <span class="block sm:inline-block">with Quebec Dev?</span></h2>
      <div class="mt-8">
        <%= link_to "Sign up for an account", new_affiliate_path, class: "bg-red-600 px-3.5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-red-700 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-indigo-600" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
